{"tid":2396225,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"譚杏藍鼓起勇氣剖白被性侵經歷！","createTime":"2021-02-05T11:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T00:07:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05fcfd152f95fb985ffa63430c12691ba701b816","tid":2396225,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T11:57:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/E8JLBTWHqTdeYOCmve7.oQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-02/fcc63240-6789-11eb-bf7b-e4d1920c9b1a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FE8JLBTWHqTdeYOCmve7.oQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-02%2Ffcc63240-6789-11eb-bf7b-e4d1920c9b1a&h=bb4f7389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌手譚杏藍（小花）昨日出片自揭在學期間曾多次被性騷擾，最嚴重的一次是慘遭迎面而來的陌生男人揸下體，情況令人髮指！小花接受東網訪時表示，片段出街後收到好多身邊的女性朋友、網民的私訊，全部都是被性騷擾的經歷：「甚至有朋友講經歷過我嘅經歷，仲問係咪好普遍，所以正正係咁，唔可以畀大家覺得係好普遍，就講出嚟！」至於一直被蒙在鼓裏的媽媽，小花說未知對方有冇睇片，暫時都未有出聲。<br />\n<br />\n她說若現時再發生同類事情、或眼見有人被性騷擾，都絕不啞忍，但不敢想像自己會做出甚麼制止行為：「比起以前我『辣』咗好多，因為以前實在太膽小，依家嘅我唔知會做啲乜，總之一定會企出嚟揭發，再衝上去幫個女仔或者男仔，一定唔會再啞忍！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/1uOmrNMi4n8kYfLncZ3sCQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEyMDA-/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-02/3ae05420-678a-11eb-9bcb-e7ef8a4d53f8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F1uOmrNMi4n8kYfLncZ3sCQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEyMDA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-02%2F3ae05420-678a-11eb-9bcb-e7ef8a4d53f8&h=eda46798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片段中小花說性騷擾經歷會成一世烙印，不過她已漸走出陰霾，幾年前調整思想，鼓起勇氣向男友及2位閨蜜剖白：「事發當刻真係驚到唔敢同任何人講，好彩身邊有佢哋聆聽，講出嚟比較容易過，其實今次拍呢條片，都有少少『餘韻』嘅感覺、回憶係衝咗上腦。」又謂最緊要從經歷中有所學習，藉被性騷擾一事，她說自此學識要為自己站出來：「因為呢啲經歷先至成就比較潑辣嘅自己。」男友聽到有何反應？小花笑指對方竟然零反應：「我同佢講嗰陣係好Casual，佢『吓』咗幾吓，大家都知呢件事已經過咗去。」"},{"pid":"183120a14019c3949384bac00f79866828e57bcf","tid":2396225,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T12:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8b086692e3cf6f895db4fdae846488215dab15","tid":2396225,"uid":160964,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T12:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/23/050049_9c2c85d99024a43e04fd153d5d52b055.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F23%2F050049_9c2c85d99024a43e04fd153d5d52b055.jpg&h=90a66299&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"013725856b11276fbbad05cc66a8f1059833e174","tid":2396225,"uid":186735,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:30:57.000Z","msg":"佢下體凸出嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8823ec64e8c6658a27044e974fe76b05ad86a58d","tid":2396225,"uid":46678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T00:07:58.000Z","msg":"佢性侵人？"}]}